For Elizabeth Otálvaro, editorial director, and Juan Maldonado, general manager of Mutante, the award is a reason for “hope” to continue working in the future.
For Otálvaro is also a “commitment and a central promise” to “generate conversations in times of such polarization and degradation of public debate”.
