The search for a gift for the daughter brought Martínez to several antique shops where she found a copy of the Voynich manuscript, considered “the most mysterious book in the world”.&nbsp; For Roberto García, responsible for the production of SER Podcast and in charge of the production and sound design of the winning work, the prize is “a joy” because he appreciates the meticulous work behind this task.
