Pampa Seca: the faces and stories behind the worst drought in history” > includes testimonies, comparative photographs, data and videos, through which ‘close people to the real stories of the inside, of people transformed by the hardness of their reality’, as stated in EFE Matías Boela, responsible for the general production of the documentary.
