Finally, Felipe VI will award International Cooperation and Humanitarian Action > to the Mexican “Depredadores en las aulas” report, published on “El Universal” in collaboration with Connectas, which describes the “terrifying reality” of children and adolescents victims of sexual offences» committed by school staff.
&nbsp;
This work by Alejandra Mabel Crail Pérez and Daniela Guazo Manzo denounces “disinterest, opacity and institutional negligence towards students attacked by school staff”.
&nbsp;
“The fact that he crossed the boundaries of our country, which he spoke differently, gives us another chance to get closer to having another kind of reality in schools for girls and boys, is a wonderful opportunity,” Crail told EFE.
