In the more than 13 thousand posts published between 1 January 2023 and 1 parity 2024, tycoon insisted on threats to its political opponents. > In August 2023 it threatened: "You persecute me, I will pursue you," written all in capital letters. In December, the tycoon had only published one word: Revenge, revenge. In a post dedicated to Special Prosecutor Jack Smith, who investigated Trump for his involvement in the facts of January 6, Trump warned that there would be "much greater percussions > than Biden and his wedge can imagine".
